items.name: Chicken Hot and Sour Soup
items.description: Indulge in the rich flavors of our chicken hot and sour soup, a tantalizing blend of spicy and tangy notes that will leave your taste buds craving for more. Perfectly balanced with tender chicken pieces and fresh vegetables, it's a comforting delight for any occasion.

items.name: Chicken Garlic Soup
items.description: Savor the comforting warmth of our chicken garlic soup, a delightful fusion of savory chicken and aromatic garlic, simmered to perfection. Bursting with flavor and wholesome goodness, it's the ultimate remedy for a chilly evening or a revitalizing lunchtime treat.

items.name: Chicken Clear Soup
items.description: Delight in the simplicity and purity of our chicken clear soup, crafted with tender chicken pieces and fresh vegetables in a light, flavorful broth. A soothing and nourishing option, perfect for a light meal or as a starter to wet your appetite.

items.name: Chicken Manchow Soup
items.description: Experience the bold and zesty flavors of our chicken manchow Soup, a tantalizing blend of succulent chicken, vibrant vegetables, and aromatic spices. This Indo Chinese favorite promises a delightful fusion of heat and tanginess, perfect for warming up any mealtime.

items.name: Chicken Ginger Soup
items.description: Relish the invigorating warmth of our chicken ginger soup, where succulent chicken meets the spicy kick of fresh ginger, creating a harmonious blend of flavors. A comforting bowlful that promises to soothe your senses and uplift your spirits with every savory sip.

items.name: Singapore Chicken Soup
items.description: Embark on a culinary journey with our Singapore chicken soup, a harmonious fusion of exotic spices, tender chicken and fragrant herbs. Inspired by the vibrant flavors of Singaporean cuisine, this aromatic soup is a tantalizing treat for the senses, perfect for those seeking a taste of the Far East.

items.name: Chicken Tandoori Leg
items.description: Savor the smoky flavors of our chicken tandoori leg, expertly marinated and grilled to perfection, offering a juicy and aromatic delight. A must-try for lovers of authentic Indian cuisine, bringing the essence of tandoori tradition to your plate.

items.name: Chicken Dana [250 grams]
items.description: Indulge in our succulent chicken dana, a [250 grams] portion of tender chicken chunks, bursting with flavor and ideal for satisfying your cravings. Perfectly seasoned and cooked to perfection, it's a delicious addition to any meal.

items.name: Chicken Tandoori Chest
items.description: Savor the exquisite flavors of our chicken tandoori chest, a generous portion of succulent chicken marinated in traditional spices and expertly grilled to perfection. Indulge in this aromatic delight, perfect for sharing or enjoying as a flavorful feast.

items.name: Special Leg
items.description: Indulge in our special veg, a culinary delight featuring succulent chicken cooked to perfection with our signature blend of spices. Treat yourself to this flavorful dish, crafted to elevate your dining experience.

items.name: Cheese Chest
items.description: Experience indulgence with our cheese chest, a delectable fusion of tender chicken and creamy cheese, perfectly grilled to create a mouthwatering delight. Savor the rich flavors of this cheesy sensation, sure to tantalize your taste buds.

items.name: Arbi Chest
items.description: Discover the unique flavors of our arbi chest, featuring tender chicken cooked to perfection with the exotic essence of arbi [taro root]. A savory delight that promises a culinary adventure for your palate.

items.name: Chicken Lollipop [6 Pieces]
items.description: Indulge in our chicken lollipop, a tantalizing treat featuring 6 perfectly seasoned and crispy chicken wings, perfect for satisfying your cravings. Enjoy the succulent flavors and crispy texture in every bite.

items.name: Chicken Tandoori
items.description: Savor the authentic flavors of our chicken tandoori, a classic Indian dish marinated in a blend of spices and grilled to perfection, offering a smoky aroma and juicy texture that delights the senses. Experience the essence of traditional Indian cuisine with every tender bite.

items.name: Pathani Dry
items.description: Delight in the bold flavors of our pathani dry, featuring tender chicken cooked with aromatic spices and herbs, creating a mouthwatering dish that's bursting with authentic pathani flavors. A savory sensation that's sure to please your palate.

items.name: Special Tikka
items.description: Experience the exquisite taste of our special tikka, where tender chicken pieces are marinated in a secret blend of spices and grilled to perfection, offering a tantalizing burst of flavor in every bite. A must-try for lovers of authentic Indian cuisine.

items.name: Chicken Paplet Tikka
items.description: Savor the culinary delight of our chicken paplet tikka, a flavorful fusion of tender chicken fillets marinated in traditional spices and grilled to perfection. Indulge in this aromatic dish that promises to tantalize your taste buds with every bite.

items.name: Tawa Fry
items.description: Experience the savory delight of our tawa fry, featuring tender chicken expertly seasoned and pan fried to perfection on a traditional griddle, offering a crispy outer texture and juicy, flavorful bites. A delicious choice for those craving authentic Indian cuisine.

items.name: Tandoori Butter Paratha
items.description: Indulge in the luxurious flavors of our tandoori butter paratha, a delectable Indian flatbread cooked in a traditional clay oven and generously brushed with creamy butter. Enjoy its flaky texture and rich, buttery taste, perfect for enhancing the enjoyment of your favorite Indian dishes or as a satisfying standalone treat.

items.name: Butter Garlic Naan
items.description: Experience the perfect harmony of flavors with our butter garlic naan, a classic Indian flatbread infused with aromatic garlic and generously brushed with creamy butter. Delight in its soft and chewy texture, complemented by the irresistible combination of garlic and butter, perfect for pairing with your favorite curries or enjoyed on its own as a delectable treat.

items.name: Roasted Papad
items.description: Enjoy the crispy delight of our roasted papad, a traditional Indian appetizer made from lentil flour and seasoned with spices, then roasted to perfection. Delight in its crunchy texture and savory flavor, perfect for starting your meal on a delicious note or as a light and satisfying snack.

items.name: Fried Papad
items.description: Indulge in the crispy goodness of our fried papad, a classic Indian appetizer made from lentil flour and deep fried to perfection. Enjoy its crunchy texture and savory flavor, perfect for complementing your meal or as a delightful standalone snack.

items.name: Chaas
items.description: Quench your thirst and refresh your palate with our chaas, a traditional Indian beverage made from yogurt blended with water and seasoned with spices like cumin and salt.
